column23: The HP Envy is a replacement for your desktop with which you perform heavy graphic tasks with. With the RX 470 video card you can play games like Overwatch on high settings and quickly watch a YouTube video while your game is minimized. Thanks to the 16GB RAM you can run several heavy programs at the same time without slowing down your laptop. The Intel i3-2200K processor ensures that your video images with programs such as Adobe Premiere Pro mount smoothly. You start-up this laptop in about 15 seconds with the 1024GB SSD drive.
